---
/**
 * BACS Labs · AlgoPanel
 *
 * "Algoritma içeriden" — 5 collapsible bölüm.
 * Pure HTML <details> kullanır, zero-JS.
 */
---

<section class="border-y border-[var(--color-border-default)] bg-[var(--color-bg-base)] py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="mb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="h-px w-12 bg-[var(--color-accent)]"></span>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
          Algoritma İçeriden
        </span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] md:text-3xl">
        Neyin <em class="not-italic text-[var(--color-accent)]">nasıl</em> hesaplandığı.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
        Standart routing API'leri köprü sınıfını bilmez. Excel bu denklemi çözemez.
        Aşağıda engine'in 5 katmanı — her birinin verisi ve mantığı açık.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <!-- 01 ─── FSM/YSS yön bazlı waypoint -->
      <details class="algo-card">
        <summary class="algo-summary">
          <span class="algo-num">01</span>
          <h3 class="algo-title">FSM/YSS yön bazlı waypoint sistemi</h3>
          <span class="algo-plus">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="algo-body">
          <p class="algo-lead">
            Her köprünün iki şeridi farklı koordinatta. Routing motoruna sadece "FSM" demek yetmez —
            <span class="hl">Asya→Avrupa</span> veya <span class="hl">Avrupa→Asya</span> şeridinin koordinatı
            ayrı verilmeli; aksi halde rota yanlış tarafa düşer ve köprüyü atlar.
          </p>
          <div class="algo-table-wrap">
            <table class="algo-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Köprü</th><th>Yön</th><th>Latitude</th><th>Longitude</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="hl">FSM</td><td>Asya → Avrupa</td><td>41.0914417</td><td>29.0618725</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">FSM</td><td>Avrupa → Asya</td><td>41.0912375</td><td>29.0617078</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">YSS</td><td>Asya → Avrupa</td><td>41.2030227</td><td>29.1123462</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">YSS</td><td>Avrupa → Asya</td><td>41.2034521</td><td>29.1106269</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">Osmangazi</td><td>Çift yön</td><td>40.7555839</td><td>29.5159248</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">1915 Çanakkale</td><td>Doğu / Batı</td><td>40.2510 / 40.2520</td><td>26.6210 / 26.6220</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="algo-callout">
            <span class="callout-arrow">→</span> Yön tespiti
            <code>planChain.direction</code> (forward / reverse)'tan gelir; long-haul rotalar için en güvenilir kaynak.
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- 02 ─── Vehicle bridge class -->
      <details class="algo-card">
        <summary class="algo-summary">
          <span class="algo-num">02</span>
          <h3 class="algo-title">8 araç sınıfı × köprü zorunluluğu</h3>
          <span class="algo-plus">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="algo-body">
          <p class="algo-lead">
            UKOME ve KGM yönetmeliği: <span class="hl">1.-2. sınıf</span> hafif vasıtalar FSM kullanabilir;
            <span class="hl">3.-5. sınıf</span> ağır vasıtalar (kamyon/TIR) <span class="hl-yss">YSS</span>'den geçmek
            <em>zorunda</em>. Yanlış araç eşlemesi → ücret yanlış hesaplanır.
          </p>
          <div class="algo-table-wrap">
            <table class="algo-table">
              <thead>
                <tr><th>Araç</th><th>KGM Sınıf</th><th>Boğaz</th><th class="num">₺/km fallback</th></tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="hl">Minivan</td><td>1.</td><td><span class="badge badge-fsm">FSM</span></td><td class="num">0,90</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">Panelvan 3,5-5t</td><td>2.</td><td><span class="badge badge-fsm">FSM</span></td><td class="num">1,05</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">Panelvan 5-7,5t · Kamyonet</td><td>2.</td><td><span class="badge badge-fsm">FSM</span></td><td class="num">1,05</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">Panelvan 5-7,5t · Kamyon</td><td>3.</td><td><span class="badge badge-yss">YSS</span></td><td class="num">1,35</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">Kamyon 7,5-12t</td><td>3.</td><td><span class="badge badge-yss">YSS</span></td><td class="num">1,35</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">Onteker 10-15t</td><td>3.</td><td><span class="badge badge-yss">YSS</span></td><td class="num">1,35</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">Kırkayak 15-20t</td><td>4.</td><td><span class="badge badge-yss">YSS</span></td><td class="num">1,75</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">TIR 22-26t</td><td>5.</td><td><span class="badge badge-yss">YSS</span></td><td class="num">2,15</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- 03 ─── KGM 2026 tarife matrisi -->
      <details class="algo-card">
        <summary class="algo-summary">
          <span class="algo-num">03</span>
          <h3 class="algo-title">KGM 2026 köprü tarifesi (₺, KDV dahil)</h3>
          <span class="algo-plus">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="algo-body">
          <p class="algo-lead">
            Sınıf × köprü matrisi. Aynı köprü için 1. sınıf ve 5. sınıf arasında <span class="hl">12,5×</span>
            fark olabilir. Yanlış sınıflandırma → ihale veya teklif başarısız.
          </p>
          <div class="algo-table-wrap">
            <table class="algo-table">
              <thead>
                <tr><th>Köprü</th><th class="num">1.</th><th class="num">2.</th><th class="num">3.</th><th class="num">4.</th><th class="num">5.</th></tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="hl">15 Temmuz Şehitler</td><td class="num">59</td><td class="num muted">—</td><td class="num muted">—</td><td class="num muted">—</td><td class="num muted">—</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">FSM</td><td class="num">59</td><td class="num">75</td><td class="num muted">—</td><td class="num muted">—</td><td class="num muted">—</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">YSS</td><td class="num">95</td><td class="num">125</td><td class="num">235</td><td class="num">595</td><td class="num">740</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">Osmangazi</td><td class="num">995</td><td class="num">1.590</td><td class="num">1.890</td><td class="num">2.505</td><td class="num">3.165</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="hl">1915 Çanakkale</td><td class="num">995</td><td class="num">1.245</td><td class="num">2.240</td><td class="num">2.490</td><td class="num">3.755</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="algo-callout">
            <span class="callout-arrow">+</span> 11 resmi KGM otoyolu (Çamlıca-Akıncı, Mahmutbey-Edirne, Çukurova hatları, vs.)
            için tam-hat ücreti ayrı tabloda; engine kaynak kodunda.
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- 04 ─── 7 case route profiles -->
      <details class="algo-card">
        <summary class="algo-summary">
          <span class="algo-num">04</span>
          <h3 class="algo-title">7 case rota profili & multi-bridge zinciri</h3>
          <span class="algo-plus">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="algo-body">
          <p class="algo-lead">
            Tek bir koridor yeterli değil. Bursa → Edirne rotası
            <span class="hl">Osmangazi + YSS</span> ister; engine bu zinciri otomatik kurar.
          </p>
          <div class="case-rows">
            <div class="case-row"><span class="case-num">01</span><span class="case-route">Güney Marmara → Avrupa</span><span class="case-chain">Osmangazi (reverse) + YSS (reverse)</span></div>
            <div class="case-row"><span class="case-num">02</span><span class="case-route">Avrupa → Güney Marmara</span><span class="case-chain">YSS (forward) + Osmangazi (forward)</span></div>
            <div class="case-row"><span class="case-num">03</span><span class="case-route">Anadolu → Çanakkale</span><span class="case-chain">YSS (reverse) + Çanakkale (forward)</span></div>
            <div class="case-row"><span class="case-num">04</span><span class="case-route">Çanakkale → Anadolu</span><span class="case-chain">Çanakkale (reverse) + YSS (forward)</span></div>
            <div class="case-row"><span class="case-num">05</span><span class="case-route">Trakya ↔ Batı Anadolu/Ege</span><span class="case-chain">1915 Çanakkale tek köprü</span></div>
            <div class="case-row"><span class="case-num">06</span><span class="case-route">Marmara ↔ Güney Marmara</span><span class="case-chain">Osmangazi tek köprü</span></div>
            <div class="case-row"><span class="case-num">07</span><span class="case-route">Şehir içi Boğaz transit</span><span class="case-chain">FSM (1.-2. sınıf) veya YSS (3.-5. sınıf)</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- 05 ─── Fuel + escalation price engine -->
      <details class="algo-card">
        <summary class="algo-summary">
          <span class="algo-num">05</span>
          <h3 class="algo-title">Akaryakıt + eskalasyon fiyat motoru</h3>
          <span class="algo-plus">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="algo-body">
          <p class="algo-lead">
            İki ipucu — akaryakıt-bazlı ve eskalasyon-bazlı —
            <span class="hl">500'e yuvarlanmış band</span> haline getirilir. Pazarda konuşulabilir, müzakere edilebilir aralık.
          </p>
          <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="formula-card">
              <div class="formula-eyebrow">Akaryakıt-bazlı</div>
              <pre class="formula-code">fuel = avgConsumption × km / 100 × ₺/L
quote = fuel / fuelShare</pre>
              <div class="formula-note">
                fuelShare: Minivan 0,44 → TIR 0,38 (sınıf büyüdükçe yakıt payı düşer)
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="formula-card">
              <div class="formula-eyebrow">Eskalasyon-bazlı</div>
              <pre class="formula-code">quote = max(km × ₺/km, minFloor)
₺/km: Minivan 11,5 → TIR 47,0</pre>
              <div class="formula-note">
                minFloor: kısa mesafelerde alt taban (Minivan 1.500 ₺ → TIR 10.500 ₺)
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="algo-callout accent">
            <span class="callout-arrow">→</span> Aralık formülü:
            <code>alt = (akaryakıt × 0,40) + (eskalasyon × 0,60)</code>, aşağı 500.
            <code>üst = (akaryakıt × 0,45) + (eskalasyon × 0,55)</code>, yukarı 500.
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Card */
  .algo-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
  }
  .algo-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-strong);
  }
  .algo-card[open] {
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
  }
  .algo-card summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .algo-card summary::marker { display: none; }

  /* Summary */
  .algo-summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .algo-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .algo-title {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .algo-title { font-size: 1.05rem; }
  }
  .algo-plus {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .algo-card[open] .algo-plus { transform: rotate(45deg); }

  /* Body */
  .algo-body {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
  }
  .algo-lead {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .hl {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .hl-yss {
    color: var(--color-route-yss);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Table */
  .algo-table-wrap {
    overflow-x: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }
  .algo-table {
    width: 100%;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }
  .algo-table th {
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    background: var(--color-bg-muted);
  }
  .algo-table th.num,
  .algo-table td.num {
    text-align: right;
  }
  .algo-table td {
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(38, 38, 38, 0.5);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  .algo-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .algo-table td.hl {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
  .algo-table td.muted {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Badge */
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1px 8px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .badge-fsm {
    background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.15);
    color: #f87171;
    border: 1px solid rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.35);
  }
  .badge-yss {
    background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.15);
    color: #4ade80;
    border: 1px solid rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.35);
  }

  /* Callout */
  .algo-callout {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 0.875rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    background: var(--color-bg-muted);
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .algo-callout.accent {
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    background: var(--color-accent-soft);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
  .algo-callout code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
  .callout-arrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  /* Case rows */
  .case-rows {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .case-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .case-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .case-route {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .case-chain {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  /* Formula card */
  .formula-card {
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }
  .formula-eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .formula-code {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    white-space: pre-wrap;
  }
  .formula-note {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
</style>
